{
  "id": 82,
  "nameSimple": "Al-Infitar",
  "nameArabic": "الإنفطار",
  "versesCount": 19,
  "revelationPlace": "makkah",
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": 5830,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "verseKey": "82:1",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 235,
      "rukuNumber": 526,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": " إِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ ٱنفَطَرَتْ",
      "pageNumber": 587,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101887,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "When the sky breaks apart",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752543,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "当苍穹破裂的时候，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5831,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "verseKey": "82:2",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 235,
      "rukuNumber": 526,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَإِذَا ٱلْكَوَاكِبُ ٱنتَثَرَتْ",
      "pageNumber": 587,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101899,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And when the stars fall, scattering,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752544,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "当众星飘堕的时候，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5832,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "verseKey": "82:3",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 235,
      "rukuNumber": 526,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَإِذَا ٱلْبِحَارُ فُجِّرَتْ",
      "pageNumber": 587,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101901,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And when the seas are erupted",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752545,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "当海洋混合的时候，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5833,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "verseKey": "82:4",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 235,
      "rukuNumber": 526,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَإِذَا ٱلْقُبُورُ بُعْثِرَتْ",
      "pageNumber": 587,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101903,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And when the [contents of] graves are scattered [i.e., exposed],",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752546,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "当坟墓被揭开的时候，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5834,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "verseKey": "82:5",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 235,
      "rukuNumber": 526,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "عَلِمَتْ نَفْسٌ مَّا قَدَّمَتْ وَأَخَّرَتْ",
      "pageNumber": 587,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101905,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "A soul will [then] know what it has put forth and kept back.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752547,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "每个人都知道自己前前后后所做的一切事情。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5835,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "verseKey": "82:6",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 235,
      "rukuNumber": 526,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ مَا غَرَّكَ بِرَبِّكَ ٱلْكَرِيمِ",
      "pageNumber": 587,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101907,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "O mankind, what has deceived you concerning your Lord, the Generous,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752548,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "人啊！什么东西引诱你背离了你的仁慈的主呢？",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5836,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "verseKey": "82:7",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 235,
      "rukuNumber": 526,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "ٱلَّذِى خَلَقَكَ فَسَوَّىٰكَ فَعَدَلَكَ",
      "pageNumber": 587,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101909,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Who created you, proportioned you, and balanced you?",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752549,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他曾创造了你，然后，使你健全，然后，使你匀称。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5837,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "verseKey": "82:8",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 235,
      "rukuNumber": 526,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فِىٓ أَىِّ صُورَةٍ مَّا شَآءَ رَكَّبَكَ",
      "pageNumber": 587,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101911,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "In whatever form He willed has He assembled you.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752550,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他意欲什么型式，就依什么型式而构造你。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5838,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "verseKey": "82:9",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 235,
      "rukuNumber": 526,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "كَلَّا بَلْ تُكَذِّبُونَ بِٱلدِّينِ",
      "pageNumber": 587,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101913,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "No! But you deny the Recompense.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752551,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "绝不然，但你们否认报应！",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5839,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "verseKey": "82:10",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 235,
      "rukuNumber": 526,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَإِنَّ عَلَيْكُمْ لَحَـٰفِظِينَ",
      "pageNumber": 587,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101888,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And indeed, [appointed] over you are keepers,<sup foot_note=230350>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752552,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你们的上面，确有许多监视者，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5840,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "verseKey": "82:11",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 235,
      "rukuNumber": 526,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "كِرَامًا كَـٰتِبِينَ",
      "pageNumber": 587,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101889,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Noble and recording;",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752553,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他们是尊贵的，是记录的，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5841,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "verseKey": "82:12",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 235,
      "rukuNumber": 526,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "يَعْلَمُونَ مَا تَفْعَلُونَ",
      "pageNumber": 587,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101890,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "They know whatever you do.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752554,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他们知道你们的一切行为。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5842,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "verseKey": "82:13",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 235,
      "rukuNumber": 526,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّ ٱلْأَبْرَارَ لَفِى نَعِيمٍ",
      "pageNumber": 587,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101891,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, the righteous will be in pleasure,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752555,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "善人们，必在恩泽中；",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5843,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "verseKey": "82:14",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 235,
      "rukuNumber": 526,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَإِنَّ ٱلْفُجَّارَ لَفِى جَحِيمٍ",
      "pageNumber": 587,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101892,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And indeed, the wicked will be in Hellfire.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752556,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "恶人们，必在烈火中。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5844,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "verseKey": "82:15",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 235,
      "rukuNumber": 526,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "يَصْلَوْنَهَا يَوْمَ ٱلدِّينِ",
      "pageNumber": 587,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101893,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "They will [enter to] burn therein on the Day of Recompense,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752557,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他们将在报应日堕入烈火，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5845,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "verseKey": "82:16",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 235,
      "rukuNumber": 526,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَمَا هُمْ عَنْهَا بِغَآئِبِينَ",
      "pageNumber": 587,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101894,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And never therefrom will they be absent.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752558,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他们绝不得离开它。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5846,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "verseKey": "82:17",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 235,
      "rukuNumber": 526,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا يَوْمُ ٱلدِّينِ",
      "pageNumber": 587,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101895,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And what can make you know what is the Day of Recompense?",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752559,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你怎能知道报应日是什么？",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5847,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "verseKey": "82:18",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 235,
      "rukuNumber": 526,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "ثُمَّ مَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا يَوْمُ ٱلدِّينِ",
      "pageNumber": 587,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101896,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Then, what can make you know what is the Day of Recompense?",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752560,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你怎能知道报应日是什么？",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5848,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "verseKey": "82:19",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 235,
      "rukuNumber": 526,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "يَوْمَ لَا تَمْلِكُ نَفْسٌ لِّنَفْسٍ شَيْـًٔا ۖ وَٱلْأَمْرُ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلَّهِ",
      "pageNumber": 587,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101897,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "It is the Day when a soul will not possess for another soul [power to do] a thing; and the command, that Day, is [entirely] with Allāh.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752561,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "在那日，任何人对任何人不能有什么裨益；在那日，命令全归安拉。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}